                <mxCell id="client_lifecycle" value="&lt;b&gt;Connection &amp; Lifecycle&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;• connect() — spawn tmux -CC via node-pty&lt;br/&gt;• disconnect() — detach &amp; kill pty&lt;br/&gt;• isConnected()&lt;br/&gt;• setVersion() / versionAtLeast()&lt;br/&gt;• requireNodePty() — locate VS Code&#39;s&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;bundled node-pty" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=4;" parent="1" vertex="1">
