                <mxCell id="client_protocol" value="&lt;b&gt;Protocol Parser&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;• ingest(raw) — buffer &amp; split lines&lt;br/&gt;• parseLine(line) — route to blocks/notifs&lt;br/&gt;• parseNotification(line) — %output,&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;%window-add, %window-close,&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;%layout-change, %exit, etc.&lt;br/&gt;• parseOutput() / parseExtendedOutput()&lt;br/&gt;• decodePaneOutput() — octal unescape&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;+ incremental UTF-8 StringDecoder" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=4;" parent="1" vertex="1">
